description.en: Bespoke kitchen splashback installation in Malvern with white subway tiles in a stacked bond pattern, contrasting charcoal grout, precision cutting around power points and window reveals, and silicone sealed edges.
description.zh: Malvern定制厨房挡水板，白色地铁砖竖直排列铺贴、炭色对比填缝、电源插座和窗框周围精准切割，以及硅胶密封收边。
